title: Indiana Dunes National Lakeshore: Guided Tours
body: Explore This Park    Plan Your Visit     Things To Do     Guided Tours              Guided Tours        Ranger-led activities and programs NPS Collection   Â    Indiana Dunes National Lakeshore offers a large number of interpretive programs and ranger-led walks and talks in various locations throughout the summer. A limited number of programs are also offered during the rest of the year.  Click here for a calendar of events or stop by the Visitor Center or Douglas Center for additional information.
